Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends},
Description: Velora Workspace battery control library
 Velora Workspace is used as the base for Velora Desktop, Mobile, and
 Bigscreen. It contains shared KCM configuration screens, applets as
 well as multiple libraries.
 .
 This package contains the battery control library files.

Package: libklipper6
